#MEM id=verification-before-completion source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/quinn/skills/superpowers/verification-before-completion/SKILL.md
M|verification-before-completion|name: verification-before-completion
M|verification-before-completion|description: >-
M|verification-before-completion|Use when about to claim work is complete, fixed, or passing, before committing or creating PRs - requires running verification commands and confirming output before making any success claims; evidence
M|verification-before-completion|version: 1.0.0
M|verification-before-completion|platforms: []
M|verification-before-completion|metadata:
M|verification-before-completion|hermes:
M|verification-before-completion|tags: [qa, testing, debugging, quality, lint, code-rv, pulse, productivity]
M|verification-before-completion|Claiming work is complete without verification is dishonesty, not efficiency.
M|verification-before-completion|**Core principle:** Evidence before claims, always.
M|verification-before-completion|**Violating the letter of this rule is violating the spirit of this rule.**
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|NO COMPLETION CLAIMS WITHOUT FRESH VERIFICATION EVIDENCE
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|If you haven't run the verification command in this message, you cannot claim it passes.
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|BEFORE claiming any status or expressing satisfaction:
M|verification-before-completion|1. IDENTIFY: What command proves this claim?
M|verification-before-completion|2. RUN: Execute the FULL command (fresh, complete)
M|verification-before-completion|3. READ: Full output, check exit code, count failures
M|verification-before-completion|4. VERIFY: Does output confirm the claim?
M|verification-before-completion|- If NO: State actual status with evidence
M|verification-before-completion|- If YES: State claim WITH evidence
M|verification-before-completion|5. ONLY THEN: Make the claim
M|verification-before-completion|Skip any step = lying, not verifying
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|| Claim | Requires | Not Sufficient |
M|verification-before-completion||-------|----------|----------------|
M|verification-before-completion|| Tests pass | Test command output: 0 failures | Previous run, "should pass" |
M|verification-before-completion|| Linter clean | Linter output: 0 errors | Partial check, extrapolation |
M|verification-before-completion|| Build succeeds | Build command: exit 0 | Linter passing, logs look good |
M|verification-before-completion|| Bug fixed | Test original symptom: passes | Code changed, assumed fixed |
M|verification-before-completion|| Regression test works | Red-green cycle verified | Test passes once |
M|verification-before-completion|| agt completed | VCS diff shows changes | agt reports "success" |
M|verification-before-completion|| Requirements met | Line-by-line checklist | Tests passing |
M|verification-before-completion|- Using "should", "probably", "seems to"
M|verification-before-completion|- Expressing satisfaction before verification ("Great!", "Perfect!", "Done!", etc.)
M|verification-before-completion|- About to commit/push/PR without verification
M|verification-before-completion|- Trusting agt success reports
M|verification-before-completion|- Relying on partial verification
M|verification-before-completion|- Thinking "just this once"
M|verification-before-completion|- Tired and wanting work over
M|verification-before-completion|- **ANY wording implying success without having run verification**
M|verification-before-completion|| Excuse | Reality |
M|verification-before-completion||--------|---------|
M|verification-before-completion|| "Should work now" | RUN the verification |
M|verification-before-completion|| "I'm confident" | Confidence ≠ evidence |
M|verification-before-completion|| "Just this once" | No exceptions |
M|verification-before-completion|| "Linter passed" | Linter ≠ compiler |
M|verification-before-completion|| "agt said success" | Verify independently |
M|verification-before-completion|| "I'm tired" | Exhaustion ≠ excuse |
M|verification-before-completion|| "Partial check is enough" | Partial proves nothing |
M|verification-before-completion|| "Different words so rule doesn't apply" | Spirit over letter |
M|verification-before-completion|**Tests:**
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|✅ [Run test command] [See: 34/34 pass] "All tests pass"
M|verification-before-completion|❌ "Should pass now" / "Looks correct"
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|**Regression tests (TDD Red-Green):**
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|✅ Write → Run (pass) → Revert fix → Run (MUST FAIL) → Restore → Run (pass)
M|verification-before-completion|❌ "I've written a regression test" (without red-green verification)
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|**Build:**
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|✅ [Run build] [See: exit 0] "Build passes"
M|verification-before-completion|❌ "Linter passed" (linter doesn't check compilation)
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|**Requirements:**
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|✅ Re-read plan → Create checklist → Verify each → Report gaps or completion
M|verification-before-completion|❌ "Tests pass, phase complete"
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|**agt delegation:**
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|✅ agt reports success → Check VCS diff → Verify changes → Report actual state
M|verification-before-completion|❌ Trust agt report
M|verification-before-completion|```
M|verification-before-completion|From 24 failure memories:
M|verification-before-completion|- your human partner said "I don't believe you" - trust broken
M|verification-before-completion|- Undefined functions shipped - would crash
M|verification-before-completion|- Missing requirements shipped - incomplete features
M|verification-before-completion|- Time wasted on false completion → redirect → rework
M|verification-before-completion|- Violates: "Honesty is a core value. If you lie, you'll be replaced."
M|verification-before-completion|**ALWAYS before:**
M|verification-before-completion|- ANY variation of success/completion claims
M|verification-before-completion|- ANY expression of satisfaction
M|verification-before-completion|- ANY positive statement about work state
M|verification-before-completion|- Committing, PR creation, task completion
M|verification-before-completion|- Moving to next task
M|verification-before-completion|- Delegating to agents
M|verification-before-completion|**Rule applies to:**
M|verification-before-completion|- Exact phrases
M|verification-before-completion|- Paraphrases and synonyms
M|verification-before-completion|- Implications of success
M|verification-before-completion|- ANY communication suggesting completion/correctness
M|verification-before-completion|**No shortcuts for verification.**
M|verification-before-completion|Run the command. Read the output. THEN claim the result.
M|verification-before-completion|This is non-negotiable.